prodNameC: 馬丁彼得泌乳激素診斷套組
ingredientsDesc: A. Anti-Prolactin coated tubes are coated with an antibody having a high affinity for human prolactin. B. Seven standards in a horse serum based matrix containing sodium azide and gentamicin sulfate are provided at the following concentrations: 0,2.5,5,10,25,50and 100 ng/mL.  C. Wash diluent is a phosphate buffered saline diluent containing polyoxyethylene sorbitan monolaurate. D. Anti-Prolactin-125I is labeled with 125I and is specific against a different epitope of the Prolactin molecule than the antibody bound to the tube. It is provided in a phosphate-albumin diluent containing sodium azide as a preservative.
applicantAddr: 新竹縣寶山鄉新竹園區創新一路６號
efficacy: 泌乳激素測試套組是專為體外定量人類血清泌乳激素的放射免疫分析法。
